data.description: Enjoy the freedoms of a lock and leave ranch in a beautifully upkept active adult neighborhood! This home is like brand new, as it has barely been lived in since it was built in 2017. The flex room is ready for your creativity to use the space as you would like. Entertaining friends or family in the open great room is easy with a large kitchen island perfect for starting conversation over hors d'oeuvres. Sit down for a meal in the dining space or warm up in the living room by the fireplace. Beyond the glass French doors, the screened in porch makes for the perfect spot to keep the party going or to relax while drinking a cup of coffee or reading a good book. The split bedroom plan allows for privacy for both the guest bedroom and master suite. The double vanity with ample counter space and large tile shower with frameless glass door make the master ensuite spa-like. The huge closet is ready for hanging all of your favorite outfits. Extra storage space in the attic can be easily accessed by a permanent staircase. This home will not last long, so schedule a private showing today!
